### LMS Backend API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 2. Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "student"
}

### 3. Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Get All Courses
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses

### 5. Create Course
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "React Mastery",
  "instructor": "Aditya Gupta",
  "description": "Learn React from scratch",
  "duration": "12 Weeks",
  "price": 2999,
  "level": "Intermediate",
  "image": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/react/react-original.svg"
}

### 6. Get Single Course
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/67041a1b2c3d4e5f6789012

### 7. Get All Students
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/students

### 8. Create Student
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Riya Sharma",
  "email": "riya@example.com",
  "phone": "+91 9876543210",
  "enrolled": "React JS",
  "status": "Active",
  "img": "https://i.pravatar.cc/150?img=2"
}

### 9. Get Single Student
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/students/67041a1b2c3d4e5f6789012

### 10. Update Course
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/67041a1b2c3d4e5f6789012
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "React Advanced",
  "price": 3499
}

### 11. Delete Course
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/67041a1b2c3d4e5f6789012

### 12. Delete Student
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/students/67041a1b2c3d4e5f6789012

